Global Pig Feed Pelleters Market Insights
Pig Feed Pelleters Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Pig Feed Pelleters Market Overview
The global pig feed pelleters market has seen significant growth in recent years, driven by the increasing demand for efficient feed processing solutions in the agriculture sector. As of 2024, the market value is estimated to be approximately USD 2.5 billion, with a projected CAGR of 4.8% from 2025 to 2030. The demand for high-quality pig feed products, improved animal nutrition, and rising pork production across the globe are major contributors to this market’s growth. The pig feed pelleters market is expected to continue expanding due to technological advancements, automation in feed production, and the rise of precision farming techniques.

